<D>__{lucky you....}
<C>__{anna}
<D>__{oh, i don't think }
<A>__{the duke grabs anna's arm and yanks her away before she can protest.}
<C>__{duke}
<D>__{if you swoon, let me know, i will catch you.}
<A>__{anna looks back at elsa, desperately.}
<C>__{elsa}
<D>__{sorry.}
<A>__{out on the dance floor: the duke showboats, but he's just awful. anna tries to make the best of it.}
