<A>__{he gets in her face, suspicious.}
<C>__{anna}
<D>__{...no.}
<C>__{duke}
<D>__{oh, all right. hang on. they don't call me the little dipper for nothing.}
<A>__{he dips anna back. elsa peeks through the crowd, can barely hold in her laughter. anna shoots elsa funny, help me looks.}
